description:
Coming Out - Program 3: Exploding the Gay Myth (with Ron Woolsey) - This is program 3 of a 13-part series produced by White Horse Media entitled, "Coming Out: Former Gays Testify of Gods Saving Love." In program 3, Steve Wohlberg interviews former gay Ron Woolsey. Homosexuality, gays, straights, love, God, sin, sex are all discussed. Order the "Coming Out" series today!

The entire 13-part "Coming Out" series is available on DVD here: https://www.whitehorsemedia.com/product/coming-out-former-gays-testify-of-gods-saving-love/. Order online or call 208-448-4446.
